social_posts.post_text: The palm trees of Palm Springs 🌴 where the wild things go 🎶

TGIF!! Dance around Joshua trees in the desert 🏜️💃🏻 = check ✅😆 #joshuatree 

Who knew the best time to visit Joshua Tree and Palm Springs was early December before all the crowds roll in? We had the hotel and pools to ourselves and were upgraded to a two bedroom suite at @villaroyale_palmsprings and roamed Joshua without any traffic 👏 it was such a treat visiting here with @fortwoplz 🌵 highly recommend a shoulder season visit to the desert 🏜️ 

#palmsprings #joshuatreenationalpark

Palm canyon trail, a super quick drive from downtown Palm Springs 🌴 highly recommend! This wasn’t on our original list of things to do but we had extra time and I’m so glad we went. Lots of easy to moderate trails in this area (Indian Canyon, Andreas Canyon) and majestic palms. Also picnic tables in the shade for a hot day in a palm oasis 🌴 if I ever go back, I’d return to this spot! 
—
#palmcanyon #palmsprings #palmtrees #palmoasis
